data.description: 55+ Active Senior Community.  Gated with large pond, clubhouse with indoor pool and hot tub and exersize room. Large party room with beautiful fir eplace and kitchen to entertain.  3 large bedrooms plus bonus room that was used by our caregiver as a bedroom, office and entertainment. 2 full baths with the primary bath wit a step-in bath and step-in shower.Friendly neighborhood and community managed HOA.Gas fireplace, private yard for your pets and large patio to BBQ. New HVAC/AC and carpeting. Updated kitchen and baths.
